(thirdQuint)Adjuvant Radiation Therapy vs.

 Watchful Waiting Following Radical Prostatectomy in High Risk Prostate Cancer.

 In this study the investigators will evaluate adjuvant radiation therapy vs.

 watchful waiting in prostate cancer patients with positive margins or capsular penetration after radical prostatectomy.

 This is a randomized, open label, multicentre, collaborative study of FinnProstate Group and Finnish Radiation Oncology group.

